# plot the scatter diagram of price-diamond characteristics
t=0
for k in ['carat','depth','table','x','y','z']:  #select one parameter for each loop
    t+=1                                         #time count
    plt.figure(t)
    plt.scatter(df[k],df['price'],s=5)           #k-th parameter -- price, size of dot is 5
    plt.xlabel(k)                                #xlabel
